      "description": "Bounce Blast combines color-based puzzle logic with satisfying physics reactions. Tap to move jelly blocks, watch them crash through obstacles, and bounce across the screen in a pinball-like frenzy!\n\nGameplay Overview\nEach tap launches a block with weight and depth that matches its number. Clear paths, unlock tunnels, and trigger chain reactions as blocks crash and transform into bouncing balls that shatter everything on the board.\n\nFeatures\n\nJelly Blocks: Soft, bouncy blocks with realistic motion and depth.\n\nTunnels: Push blocks through tunnels that spawn new ones as you clear the front.\n\nBlockers: Hidden, locked, and question-mark blocks add puzzle strategy.\n\nVaried Levels: From simple grids to maze-like stages with shifting mechanics.\n\nPhysics Reactions: Blocks break apart and rebound to create chain combos.\n\nHundreds of Levels: Progress through easy starts to mind-bending challenges.\n\nDaily Challenges: Fresh levels every day to test your skills.\n\nEnjoy the perfect balance of logic and chaos \u2014 simple to play, endlessly satisfying to master.",
      "subtitle": "Bounce Balls and Blast Cubes",
      "promo_text": "A satisfying hybrid puzzle where jelly blocks crash, bounce, and burst through colorful levels filled with tunnels and blockers!",
